\title{Period of a Markov Chain}
\taxon{definition}

\transclude{ShanghaiTech-SI140A-001E}

\p{
  A Markov chain is \strong{periodic} if it is [irreducible](ShanghaiTech-SI140A-001D) and all states have period greater than 1.
}

\p{
  A Markov chain is \strong{aperiodic} if it is [irreducible](ShanghaiTech-SI140A-001D) and all states have period 1.
}
